    "description": "The Solidigm SSD D7-D4512 Series is a PCIe* Gen3 SSD architected with a dual-port, NVMe* (Non-Volatile Memory Express*) controller delivering leading performance, low latency, and high availability. Matching the performance with world-class reliability and endurance, Solidigm SSD D7-D4512 Series offers a range of capacities - 1.92 TB, 3.84 TB, 7.68 TB, and 15.36 TB. With PCIe Gen 3 support and NVMe specification 1.2b implementation, the Solidigm SSD D7-D4512 Series is designed to support active/active dual port and recovery during fail over when one of the hosts becomes unavailable.",
